ygData.messageBody:
Hi everyone, just joined up in this club and hope
to make some friends. I have Characters on 4

warrior on Veeshan. I'll get back to you with my other
servers cause I'm not quite sure how to spell them, Let
me know if anyone else pays on veeshan, or let me
know what severs you play one, I'm willing to
relocate(won't take too long, got lvl 14 in less than 2 days),
just gotta know where and how to hunt like those
people of the higher lvls. Anyway I'm gonna quit talking
and start playing everquest after I eat real quick,
so Peace!
